# Quant Review Platform — Team Composition Overview
> **CTO Strategic Document** · Grounded in Cognitive Science Synthesis · CONFIDENTIAL

---

## Executive Summary

This document defines the full team composition required to build Quant Review into a genuine learning engine — not merely a content delivery platform. Every role and responsibility below is grounded in the six-book cognitive science synthesis:

- *Make It Stick*
- *How We Learn*
- *Moonwalking with Einstein*
- *Reality Is Broken*
- *Building a Second Brain*
- *Uncommon Sense Teaching*

The **five highest-impact features** identified by the synthesis:

| # | Feature |
|---|---------|
| 1 | SM-2 extended to problems |
| 2 | Cross-chapter interleaved practice |
| 3 | Time and error tracking |
| 4 | Gamification layer with fiero moments |
| 5 | Prerequisite gating |

These require **8 distinct functional areas** to execute correctly.

