## Team Overview Matrix

| Role | Dept | Difficulty | Primary Mandate |
|------|------|------------|-----------------|
| Lead Full-Stack Engineer | Engineering | 🔴 High | Architectural owner of the entire platform |
| AI / ML Engineer | Engineering | 🔴 High | Owns LLMs, adaptive intelligence, and ingestion pipeline |
| Cognitive Science & Curriculum Lead | Product / Content | 🔴 High | Bridges learning science and product |
| Gamification & UX Designer | Product / Design | 🟡 Medium | Owns emotional and motivational layer |
| Frontend Engineer | Engineering | 🟡 Medium | Executes design system, all user-facing components |
| Data / Analytics Engineer | Engineering / Growth | 🟡 Medium | Owns data infrastructure that makes the platform adaptive |
| Quant Content Author | Content | 🟢 Low | Authors, reviews, and tags all quant problems and flashcards |
| Growth & Community Manager | Growth | 🟢 Low | Owns distribution, community, and social connectivity layer |

> **Note on difficulty ratings:** Difficulty reflects cognitive and technical complexity of the task set, not seniority. A "Low" difficulty role requires domain expertise; it does not require systems-level problem solving under ambiguity.

