## Phased Hiring Plan

### Phase 1 — Foundation (Months 1–3)
**Hire:** Lead Full-Stack Engineer, AI/ML Engineer, Cognitive Science & Curriculum Lead

These three roles build the core learning engine: SM-2 for problems, interleaved practice, document ingestion pipeline, and the prerequisite architecture. Nothing else ships until this is solid.

### Phase 2 — Experience Layer (Months 3–6)
**Hire:** Gamification & UX Designer, Frontend Engineer, Data/Analytics Engineer

The learning mechanics need a motivational layer (fiero, XP, focus mode) and the data infrastructure to measure whether they're working. Bring these in once the backend learning engine is stable.

### Phase 3 — Scale (Months 6+)
**Hire:** Quant Content Authors (contract), Growth & Community Manager

Content volume and distribution are growth problems, not architecture problems. Solve architecture first, then pour fuel on it.

